This paper presents a new algorithm for sample-efficient learning of CVaR-optimal policies in Markov decision processes. The paper focuses on reinforcement learning approaches and explores risk-sensitive objectives such as conditional value at risk (CVaR). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.ML), robotics (cs.RO), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
